data.description: This well-maintained, spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on a peaceful, serene street tucked away in a tranquil neighborhood with no Hoa. It features a split floor plan and a spacious fenced backyard with plenty of room for your RV, boat, and more catering to the outdoor enthusiasts!. Elegant tile and laminate flooring throughout, combining style and easy maintenance. There is quick access to major highways, streamlining your daily commute and close proximity to essential amenities, including supermarkets, dining establishments, and entertainment venues.Schedule a tour and come and experience firsthand what could be your dream home!
